SUB_W11_EVAR_DIVA_LOVE_100_CUT_000_020.text:
Oh dear, this could be a proper mess;
I won't be of much use in a trial that's
all about emotions.

SUB_W11_EVAR_DIVA_LOVE_100_CUT_000_070.text:
Worry not, Lela. Merely plant the seeds.
You are chosen by the god of the Imeru;
the markings on your face serve as proof.

SUB_W11_EVAR_DIVA_LOVE_110_CUT_010_040.text:
Since I lack a heart, ye will have
to be the one to plant the seeds;
they'll not bloom if I do it.
